content.speaker: Mr. GREEN of Texas
content.text:
Mr. GREEN of Texas. Madam Speaker, I move that the House do now 
adjourn.

content.speaker: The RECORDER
content.text:
The motion was agreed to; accordingly (at 7 o'clock and 36 minutes 
p.m.), under its previous order, the House adjourned until tomorrow, 
Thursday, February 6, 2020, at 10 a.m. for morning-hour debate.
